That&#39;s easy in Bixby.  If you make an input to your action required...it will prompt the user for input.  Let&#39;s say you have an action like this:

    action (FindSomething) {
      type(Search)
      description (Search for something)
      
      collect {
        input (search) {
          type (Search)
          min (Required) max (One) // Force Bixby to prompt for an input.
        }
      }
